description:
Authenticator to generate 2-step verification codes using your YubiKey

Authenticator to generate 2-step verification codes using your YubiKey
- Settings are now a separate section from the Home view
- Android: Added PIV support
- Improvements to YubiKey connections used over USB to help with permissions issues (desktop)
- Theme colors have been tweaked for improved contrast (a11y)
- New translations: Greek, Ukrainian, Russian
- Binaries compiled with Flutter 3.35.3 and Python 3.13.7 (desktop)
- Various other fixes and improvements
